;唐卡士打
2008年7月30日，[[英超|英超]]曼城宣佈以30萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉會費讓早一個球季以借將身份協助唐卡士打升上[[英冠|英冠]]的米斯正式加盟，米斯與唐卡士打簽約三年<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Matt Mills joins Doncaster |url=http://www.mcfc.co.uk/news/club-news/2008/july/matt-mills-joins-doncaster |publisher=''mcfc.co.uk'' |date=30 July 2008 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |archive-date=2012-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120806092608/http://www.mcfc.co.uk/News/Club-news/2008/July/Matt-Mills-joins-Doncaster |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;雷丁
2009年8月5日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會雷丁據報以200萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]轉會費從同是[[英冠|英冠]]的唐卡士打購入米斯，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Matt Mills joins Brendan's Babes |url=http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/matt-mills-joins-brendans-babes-4235647 |publisher=''getreading.co.uk'' |date=5 August 2009 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305013808/http://www.getreading.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/matt-mills-joins-brendans-babes-4235647 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;李斯特城
2011年7月8日，[[英冠|英冠]]球會李斯特城從同是[[英冠|英冠]]的雷丁購入米斯，轉會費金額沒有正式公佈，據消息透露金額為450萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]另有附加條件，最終有機會超過500萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，如果確實的話將會打破李斯特城球會紀錄，合約為期四年<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Defender Matt Mills leaves Reading for Leicester City |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14064234 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=8 July 2011 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |archive-date=2012-02-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120223091518/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/14064234 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。之從更任命為李斯特城隊長<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Matt Mills so honoured to be captain of Leicester City |url=http://www.thisisleicestershire.co.uk/Matt-Mills-honoured-captain-Leicester-City/story-13126278-detail/story.html#axzz2W6mfex5a |publisher=''thisisleicestershire.co.uk'' |date=31 August 2011 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110908065841/http://www.thisisleicestershire.co.uk/Matt-Mills-honoured-captain-Leicester-City/story-13126278-detail/story.html#axzz2W6mfex5a |archivedate=2011年9月8日 }}</ref>。

2012年3月2日, 於季中擔任李斯特城領隊的[[尼格尔·皮尔逊|-{zh-cn:尼格尔·皮尔逊;zh-hk:尼祖·皮雅臣}-]]證實[[英冠|英冠]]里茲聯對米斯有興趣，另報章披露米斯曾與領隊爭吵，其於球會位置受到影響<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Leicester's Nigel Pearson says Leeds want Matt Mills |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17225020 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=2 March 2012 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |archive-date=2012-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305090541/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/17225020 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;博尔顿
2012年7月4日，剛降落[[英冠|英冠]]的博尔顿簽入李斯特城25歲[[後衛_(足球)#中后卫|中堅]]米斯，轉會費金額沒有透露，合約為期三年<ref>{{cite web |language=en |title=Bolton Wanderers sign defender Matt Mills from Leicester City |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18503575 |publisher=''[[BBC_Sport|BBC Sport]]'' |date=4 July 2012 |accessdate=13 June 2013 |archive-date=2012-08-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120826114911/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/18503575 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

